data.title: RSE Fellows - 1783 - 2002 - Summary
data.meta_description: RSE Fellows - 1783 -2002 - Summary - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document lists over 200 former fellows of the Royal Society of Edinburgh from 1783 to 2002. It provides names, dates of birth and death, place of birth, date of election, profession, and occasional notes for each fellow. The fellows came from a wide range of backgrounds and professions, including royal family members, physicians, engineers, mathematicians, astronomers, and more.
